<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pc43d6ed7" data-block-id="43d6ed7"><div class="pc43d6ed7__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">Confidentiality</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph -->

<!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"43fdddd","css":".pc43fdddd{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:8px 0px 0px 24px !important;}.pc43fdddd__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pc43fdddd .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:Readex Pro;font-weight:300;}@media screen and (max-width: 767px){.pc43fdddd .pc-paragraph{font-size:14px;}}","content":"In case of need, the project manager will sign an additional NDA contract and will not be allowed to share any confidential information about the project with anyone without the Client’s approval. Confidential information does not include information that: - the project manager knew before the Client disclosed it; - is or becomes public knowledge through no fault of the project manager; - the project manager obtains from sources other than the Client.","fontSizeMobile":14,"fontWeight":"300","fontFamily":"Readex Pro","margin":{"top":"8px","right":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"24px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pc43fdddd" data-block-id="43fdddd"><div class="pc43fdddd__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">In case of need, the project manager will sign an additional NDA contract and will not be allowed to share any confidential information about the project with anyone without the Client’s approval. Confidential information does not include information that: - the project manager knew before the Client disclosed it; - is or becomes public knowledge through no fault of the project manager; - the project manager obtains from sources other than the Client.</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/container -->

