<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"b81376f","css":".pcb81376f{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pcb81376f__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pcb81376f .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:Readex Pro;font-weight:400;}@media screen and (max-width: 767px){.pcb81376f .pc-paragraph{font-size:14px;}}","content":"Ownership","fontSizeMobile":14,"fontFamily":"Readex Pro"} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pcb81376f" data-block-id="b81376f"><div class="pcb81376f__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">Ownership</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph -->

<!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"9714374","css":".pc9714374{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:8px 0px 0px 24px !important;}.pc9714374__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pc9714374 .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:Readex Pro;font-weight:300;}@media screen and (max-width: 767px){.pc9714374 .pc-paragraph{font-size:14px;}}","content":"After the project is completed and the total amount for the project is paid in full, the client receives rights to all the designs produced. The Client guarantees that they have legal rights to all elements of text, photographs, and anything else that they provide the Designer with, and will not hold the Designer responsible for any third-party claims. The project manager will guarantee that they have legal rights to all elements related to the services they are providing and will not hold the Client responsible for any third-party claims.","fontSizeMobile":14,"fontWeight":"300","fontFamily":"Readex Pro","margin":{"top":"8px","right":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"24px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pc9714374" data-block-id="9714374"><div class="pc9714374__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">After the project is completed and the total amount for the project is paid in full, the client receives rights to all the designs produced. The Client guarantees that they have legal rights to all elements of text, photographs, and anything else that they provide the Designer with, and will not hold the Designer responsible for any third-party claims. The project manager will guarantee that they have legal rights to all elements related to the services they are providing and will not hold the Client responsible for any third-party claims.</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"constrained"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"1be7810","css":".pc1be7810{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:16px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pc1be7810__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pc1be7810 .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:Readex Pro;font-weight:400;}@media screen and (max-width: 767px){.pc1be7810 .pc-paragraph{font-size:14px;}}","content":"Out-of-Scope Requirements","fontSizeMobile":14,"fontFamily":"Readex Pro","margin":{"top":"16px","right":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"0px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pc1be7810" data-block-id="1be7810"><div class="pc1be7810__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">Out-of-Scope Requirements</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph -->

<!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"4cd54d5","css":".pc4cd54d5{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:8px 0px 0px 24px !important;}.pc4cd54d5__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pc4cd54d5 .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:Readex Pro;font-weight:300;}@media screen and (max-width: 767px){.pc4cd54d5 .pc-paragraph{font-size:14px;}}","content":"The project manager is not responsible for professional branding, copywriting, and illustration services. If in the process any of those appear needed, we’ll need to find extra relevant people to cooperate with.","fontSizeMobile":14,"fontWeight":"300","fontFamily":"Readex Pro","margin":{"top":"8px","right":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"24px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pc4cd54d5" data-block-id="4cd54d5"><div class="pc4cd54d5__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">The project manager is not responsible for professional branding, copywriting, and illustration services. If in the process any of those appear needed, we’ll need to find extra relevant people to cooperate with.</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"constrained"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"f3f0f95","css":".pcf3f0f95{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:16px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pcf3f0f95__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pcf3f0f95 .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:Readex Pro;font-weight:400;}@media screen and (max-width: 767px){.pcf3f0f95 .pc-paragraph{font-size:14px;}}","content":"Breach of Agreement","fontSizeMobile":14,"fontFamily":"Readex Pro","margin":{"top":"16px","right":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"0px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pcf3f0f95" data-block-id="f3f0f95"><div class="pcf3f0f95__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">Breach of Agreement</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph -->

<!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"ce5cd68","css":".pcce5cd68{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:8px 0px 0px 24px !important;}.pcce5cd68__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pcce5cd68 .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:Readex Pro;font-weight:300;}@media screen and (max-width: 767px){.pcce5cd68 .pc-paragraph{font-size:14px;}}","content":"Once the project is completed, the Client must pay the remainder of the cost. Failure to pay the remaining means that the Designer will retain the rights to all the designs produced along the project and will be able to break the confidentiality contract. If the client rejects the designs, the client is not allowed to use any designs produced. Should there be a desire to terminate the agreement before the completion of the project, the Client will notify the Designer 5 days in advance, and pay for services already completed and for hours already worked.","fontSizeMobile":14,"fontWeight":"300","fontFamily":"Readex Pro","margin":{"top":"8px","right":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"24px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pcce5cd68" data-block-id="ce5cd68"><div class="pcce5cd68__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">Once the project is completed, the Client must pay the remainder of the cost. Failure to pay the remaining means that the Designer will retain the rights to all the designs produced along the project and will be able to break the confidentiality contract. If the client rejects the designs, the client is not allowed to use any designs produced. Should there be a desire to terminate the agreement before the completion of the project, the Client will notify the Designer 5 days in advance, and pay for services already completed and for hours already worked.</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"constrained"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"6b62b06","css":".pc6b62b06{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:16px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pc6b62b06__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pc6b62b06 .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:Readex Pro;font-weight:400;}@media screen and (max-width: 767px){.pc6b62b06 .pc-paragraph{font-size:14px;}}","content":"Additional Scope","fontSizeMobile":14,"fontFamily":"Readex Pro","margin":{"top":"16px","right":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"0px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pc6b62b06" data-block-id="6b62b06"><div class="pc6b62b06__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">Additional Scope</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph -->

<!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"f695d33","css":".pcf695d33{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:8px 0px 0px 24px !important;}.pcf695d33__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pcf695d33 .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:Readex Pro;font-weight:300;}@media screen and (max-width: 767px){.pcf695d33 .pc-paragraph{font-size:14px;}}","content":"Any additions to the scope of the project can be denied by a service provider. If the client still wants to add extra scope, the Client must send the details needed to initiate an additional project. At that point, the Designer will provide another invoice with the cost for the additional deliverables. Anything that is not covered under the deliverable items is considered outside the scope.","fontSizeMobile":14,"fontWeight":"300","fontFamily":"Readex Pro","margin":{"top":"8px","right":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"24px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pcf695d33" data-block-id="f695d33"><div class="pcf695d33__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">Any additions to the scope of the project can be denied by a service provider. If the client still wants to add extra scope, the Client must send the details needed to initiate an additional project. At that point, the Designer will provide another invoice with the cost for the additional deliverables. Anything that is not covered under the deliverable items is considered outside the scope.</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/container -->

