<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-heading pc34bcc41" data-block-id="34bcc41"><div class="pc34bcc41__overlay"><h2 class="pc-heading">Project Billing</h2></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/heading -->

<!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"d1d873f","css":".pcd1d873f{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pcd1d873f__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pcd1d873f .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#000000;font-size:14px;font-family:Readex Pro;font-weight:300;}@media screen and (max-width: 767px){.pcd1d873f .pc-paragraph{font-size:14px;}}","content":"If you are unhappy about the progress of the project, feel we are not finding an appropriate angle, and/or feel that you voice and input is not being acknowledged, kindly discuss this with me. I would encourage that we schedule a call rather than e-mail ; I am very easy going and even easier to talk to.","fontSizeMobile":14,"fontWeight":"300","fontFamily":"Readex Pro"} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pcd1d873f" data-block-id="d1d873f"><div class="pcd1d873f__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">If you are unhappy about the progress of the project, feel we are not finding an appropriate angle, and/or feel that you voice and input is not being acknowledged, kindly discuss this with me. I would encourage that we schedule a call rather than e-mail ; I am very easy going and even easier to talk to.</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph -->

